{"tid":2412708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部營商指引刪「國際金融中心」 英貶香港為區域樞紐","createTime":"2021-02-18T07:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T08:37:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"70fcb5357ee5bd02c86cddcc139249887a32419b","tid":2412708,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:35:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/ONIXJBP4XNFPJDXSNENLCN2EWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FONIXJBP4XNFPJDXSNENLCN2EWI%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOjnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=f8361e84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FONIXJBP4XNFPJDXSNENLCN2EWI%2F&h=edc0b7c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/ONIXJBP4XNFPJDXSNENLCN2EWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n外交部營商指引刪「國際金融中心」<br />\n英貶香港為區域樞紐<br />\n<br />\n【兩制蓋棺】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】北京強推港版國安法，國際社會擔心香港自由、自治不保，一國兩制下的保障逐漸消失。英國外交部本周二更新了與香港的營商指引，由過去形容香港為「國際金融中心（international financial centre）」貶為「國際商業樞紐（global business hub）」，提到香港向來吸引國際訪客時更用上「區域樞紐（regional hub）」；與港府有正面、前瞻性的關係等字眼亦遭刪去，同時不再直接描述香港享有高度自治。有前經濟師指此舉反映英方或覺得香港不再是吸引國際投資者立足之地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o3GBuAh6-1LP66rsDGNXaVOiLNk=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5BNW4O4I5VHUBLKB3NBA6QUETU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo3GBuAh6-1LP66rsDGNXaVOiLNk%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5BNW4O4I5VHUBLKB3NBA6QUETU.jpg&h=b1dc151b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■英國外交部新營商指引指香港高度自治不再；圖為英外交部長藍韜文。<br />\n<br />\n據報今次是英國外交部自2019年8月後，再度更新與香港的營商指引，而這次更涉及多個方面。新指引特別提到國安法在港實施、容許不公開審訊或送中審訊、四名民主派議員被取消資格、以及BNO簽證等內容，並且引述英國的香港半年報告，批評國安法削弱港人行使基本權利和自由，又重申國安法和DQ民主派議員違反《中英聯合聲明》。<br />\n<br />\n此外，新指引認為香港的言論自由令人關注，甚至有表面證據顯示有公司因為僱員的政見、參與示威，而受到中國當局的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JvszSU80v7Q9Q7bjwKAgmrY-BYw=/2540x1117/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T6JQYHOL4NDIZGA5XRHQ36HXQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJvszSU80v7Q9Q7bjwKAgmrY-BYw%3D%2F2540x1117%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT6JQYHOL4NDIZGA5XRHQ36HXQE.jpg&h=73022c76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新指引提到國安法實施、四名民主派議員被DQ等內容，指違反《中英聯合聲明》，並且形容港人權利自由被削弱。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DBts_Cc38srLHNHiLdK4_uUwylo=/551x853/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3X5T4ZHGMJAEDFJX6XTYOQUXHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDBts_Cc38srLHNHiLdK4_uUwylo%3D%2F551x853%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3X5T4ZHGMJAEDFJX6XTYOQUXHA.jpg&h=80fa03fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家：反映對港意識形態改變<br />\n<br />\n原本的指引形容香港在防務和外交範疇外，例如經濟及貿易享有高度自治，新指引不再直接描述香港有高度自治，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n前香港滙豐環球市場經濟師林浩波。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，英國外交部在指引刪除香港是「。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林續指，上述改變符合近日在港。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府回覆稱，指引內容有關國。。。。。。"},{"pid":"3f8e6bb06beb0a5f90708162008f6aae8577a33d","tid":2412708,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:37:28.000Z","msg":"下次就係小漁村"}]}